py-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104woi1665702807515.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/woi1665702807515.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/woi1665702807515.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"woi1665702807515\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Data Type\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Uniface data type of the parameter. The data type and implementation determine the other properties that can be set for this parameter.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"woi1665702807515__section_ebs_jgq_dxb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d737557e51\">Applies To</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"woi1665702807515__ul_a12_kgq_dxb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"woi1665702807515__li_d42827e1_d42828e1_d42829e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jha1665702714162.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jha1665702714162.html\" title=\"A Signature Parameter is a Development Object that describes an argument that can be passed in or out of an operation.\">Signature Parameter</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dld1665702530483.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Uniface Data Types</a><p>Data types are classifications for data containers, such as fields, variables, parameters, and return values. They define the characteristics of the data and determine how the data is handled during processing and storage. Unifac